Package: bfasttools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for BFAST spatial analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author@R: person("Justin", "Nghiem", email="justinnghiem@berkeley.edu", role=c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of functions to perform Breaks for Additive Season and Trend (BFAST) analysis on spatial datasets.
    This package builds on the "bfast" R package (available on CRAN) to extend use to spatial datasets, and has been especially
    tailored for MODIS data. It takes advantage of parallel computing to more efficiently run code from "bfast" over many cells
    in raster datasets.
